snippet.title: Witch's Tale
snippet.description:
Play iOS: https://bigfi.sh/2yNXDew

Discover the latest puzzle game from the TOP SELLING premium games company, Big Fish. With more than 26 million premium game downloads worldwide, Big Fish gives you exciting new games to solve each week!

Help remove a curse from an evil witch in this spellbinding Hidden Object game! Circe was once your mentor, but when she hatches a heinous plan to wed a prince, turning them into frogs until one agrees to marry her, you find yourself fighting to save your kingdom! Master your magical skills as you solve amazing puzzles and hunt through fascinating hidden object scenes in a face-off against your greatest enemy, the one that taught you everything you know! 

Features: 
• Over a dozen different challenge types!
• More than 90 levels to play!
• Multiple levels of difficulties!
